Package com.vk2gpz.tokenenchant.api

Class EnchantInfo

java.lang.Object
com.vk2gpz.tokenenchant.api.EnchantInfo
public class EnchantInfo
extends java.lang.Object
Holds the very basic information about an enchantment listed in the config.yml.

Currently, all custom enchantments need to be listed under "Potions:" section in the config.yml.
